}}'''摩洛哥与以色列的关系'''是指[[以色列|以色列]]和[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]之间的雙邊关系。

1948年以色列建國當年發生[[1948年摩洛哥反猶暴動|1948年摩洛哥反猶暴動]]，促使[[犹太人|犹太人]]逃离摩洛哥<ref>{{Cite web|title=Oujda & Djerada Victims|url=https://www.sephardicgen.com/databases/oujdaDjeradaSrchFrm.html|accessdate=2020-12-13|work=www.sephardicgen.com|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210213509/https://www.sephardicgen.com/databases/oujdaDjeradaSrchFrm.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

虽然摩洛哥在與以色列建交前不承认以色列是一个国家，不過摩洛哥國王[[哈桑二世_(摩洛哥)|哈桑二世]]在{{link-en|1965年卡萨布兰卡阿拉伯联盟会议|1965 Arab League summit}}上邀请了[[以色列情報及特殊使命局|摩萨德]]和[[以色列國家安全局|以色列國家安全局]]特工，哈桑二世与以色列情报部门建立了秘密的互惠关系，以色列情报部门在法国[[巴黎|巴黎]]绑架摩洛哥持不同政见者和左翼反对派领导人{{link-en|迈赫迪·本·巴尔卡|Mehdi Ben Barka}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=History : 1965, when the Mossad helped Morocco murder Ben Barka|url=https://en.yabiladi.com/articles/details/58726/history-1965-when-mossad-helped.html|accessdate=2020-12-13|last=Yabiladi.com|work=en.yabiladi.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421021325/https://en.yabiladi.com/articles/details/58726/history-1965-when-mossad-helped.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|迈赫迪·本·巴尔卡|Mehdi Ben Barka}}最後下落不明。而兩國的秘密關係对以色列在[[六日战争|六日战争]]中重创[[埃及|埃及]]、[[约旦|约旦]]和[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]起到了重要作用<ref>{{Cite web|title=Morocco tipped off Israeli intelligence, ‘helped Israel win Six Day War’|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/morocco-tipped-off-israeli-intelligence-helped-israel-win-six-day-war/|accessdate=2020-12-13|last=Surkes|first=Sue|work=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108135907/https://www.timesofisrael.com/morocco-tipped-off-israeli-intelligence-helped-israel-win-six-day-war/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1975年，西撒哈拉战争爆发後，摩洛哥再度寻求以色列情报部门的秘密援助，以色列情报部门幫助摩洛哥組建[[摩洛哥皇家軍隊|摩洛哥皇家軍隊]]和[[摩洛哥墙|摩洛哥墙]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Western Sahara’s struggle for freedom cut off by a wall|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2015/6/5/western-saharas-struggle-for-freedom-cut-off-by-a-wall|accessdate=2020-12-13|last=McNeish|first=Hannah|work=www.aljazeera.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211231144/https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2015/6/5/western-saharas-struggle-for-freedom-cut-off-by-a-wall|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1980年代，哈桑二世试图承认以色列，于1986年在[[拉巴特|拉巴特]]与以色列总理[[希蒙·佩雷斯|希蒙·佩雷斯]]会面，但遭到[[阿拉伯联盟|阿拉伯联盟]]和摩洛哥人的抗议，迫使哈桑二世放棄承認<ref>{{Cite news|title=PERES AND HASSAN IN TALKS; SYRIA BREAKS MOROCCAN TIES (Published 1986)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1986/07/23/world/peres-and-hassan-in-talks-syria-breaks-moroccan-ties.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=1986-07-23|accessdate=2020-12-13|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Judith|last=Miller|first2=Special To the New York|last2=Times|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211080856/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/07/23/world/peres-and-hassan-in-talks-syria-breaks-moroccan-ties.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過哈桑二世与佩雷斯依舊保持着联系。1999年哈桑二世去世时，佩雷斯向其表示哀悼<ref>{{Cite news|title=Hassan II of Morocco Dies at 70; A Monarch Oriented to the West (Published 1999)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1999/07/24/world/hassan-ii-of-morocco-dies-at-70-a-monarch-oriented-to-the-west.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=1999-07-24|accessdate=2020-12-13|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Joseph R.|last=Gregory|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210165354/https://www.nytimes.com/1999/07/24/world/hassan-ii-of-morocco-dies-at-70-a-monarch-oriented-to-the-west.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在兩國秘密關係下，[[以色列护照|以色列护照]]持有者被允許进入摩洛哥，並可获得摩洛哥签证<ref>{{Cite web|title=What it’s like to travel the world as a Palestinian on an Israeli passport|url=https://qz.com/1445321/what-its-like-to-travel-on-an-israeli-passport-as-a-palestinian/|accessdate=2020-12-13|last=Mhajne|first=Anwar|work=Quartz|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327134352/https://qz.com/1445321/what-its-like-to-travel-on-an-israeli-passport-as-a-palestinian/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年12月10日，以色列和摩洛哥同意建立外交关系<ref>{{Cite news|title=Morocco joins other Arab nations agreeing to normalize Israel ties|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/israel-usa-morocco-int-idUSKBN28K2CW|newspaper=Reuters|date=2020-12-10|accessdate=2020-12-13|language=en|first=Steve|last=Holland|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214174740/https://www.reuters.com/article/israel-usa-morocco-int-idUSKBN28K2CW|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国也将承认摩洛哥对[[西撒哈拉|西撒哈拉]]地区的主權主张<ref>{{Cite web|title=以色列与摩洛哥恢复外交关系，美国将承认摩洛哥对西撒哈拉地区的主张|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-11/doc-iiznezxs6327305.shtml|accessdate=2020-12-13|date=2020-12-11|last=国际金融报|publisher=新浪财经|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216014001/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-11/doc-iiznezxs6327305.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

